      <title>阿曼 OQ 甲醇工厂首次公开募股 (IPO) 募资 4.89 亿美元后股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/oman-oq-methanol-unit-falls-10-in-debut-after-489-million-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OQ Base Industries 在马斯喀特进行 4.89 亿美元的首次公开募股后，其股价在首日交易中下跌，这是中东地区一系列早盘交易不佳的上市公司中最新的一家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/oman-oq-methanol-unit-falls-10-in-debut-after-489-million-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 07:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>24 小时降息结束全球央行宽松政策年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年是通货膨胀率下降到足以让大多数发达经济体开始放松货币政策的一年，而随着美联储牵头的 24 小时连续决策，这一年即将结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
